OL,3,CAirport staff urged to earn '#200 per
OL,4,Cflight' from oversized bags
OL,6,FAirport workers are being encouraged
OL,7,Fto charge passengers for oversized
OL,8,Fbags with a per-flight target,
OL,9,Faccording to a leaked staff poster.
OL,11,FThe notice from Jersey Airport, which
OL,12,Fwas shared anonymously on a popular
OL,13,Flocal Facebook group, says: "KEEP IT
OL,14,FUP!!! Let's hit EasyJet revenue
OL,15,Ftarget!!
OL,17,F"Let's hit #200 revenue per flight
OL,18,F!!!!"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
