PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778220033
OL,3,CAirport staff urged to earn '#200 per
OL,4,Cflight' from oversized bags
OL,6,FIt is accompanied by a series of
OL,7,Fpictures including a hand baggage
OL,8,Fsizer, a common sight at check-in, and
OL,9,Fa card machine next to a hand holding
OL,10,Fmoney.
OL,12,FIn response, the airline says: "This
OL,13,Fis not an easyJet poster and easyJet
OL,14,Fdoes not set bag charge targets.
OL,16,F"As soon as we were made aware of this
OL,17,Fsign at Jersey Airport, we instructed
OL,18,Fthe ground handler to remove it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
