PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778220033
OL,3,CAirport staff urged to earn '#200 per
OL,4,Cflight' from oversized bags
OL,6,FeasyJet does not employ or manage its
OL,7,Fground handling staff directly,
OL,8,Fchoosing to contract the work out to
OL,9,Fthird parties such as Swissport in
OL,10,FJersey.
OL,12,FThe airline maintains customers will
OL,13,Fonly be charged for luggage that is
OL,14,Foversized or beyond their allowance,
OL,15,Fwith their priority to fit bags on
OL,16,Fboard and to be fair to those who have
OL,17,Fpaid for extra space.
OL,19,FIt adds that the sign does not
OL,20,Frepresent the company's policy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
