PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778220033
OL,3,CAirport staff urged to earn '#200 per
OL,4,Cflight' from oversized bags
OL,6,FHowever, Swissport says: "We comply
OL,7,Fwith airlines' baggage policies. As a
OL,8,Fground handler, we are contracted to
OL,9,Fdo so.
OL,11,F"The old sign has been removed."
OL,13,FA Ports of Jersey spokesperson adds:
OL,14,F"Passenger experience is very
OL,15,Fimportant to us, including the clarity
OL,16,Fof information presented within the
OL,17,Fairport environment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1778220033
OL,3,CAirport staff urged to earn '#200 per
OL,4,Cflight' from oversized bags
OL,6,F"The sign referenced appeared in a non-
OL,7,Fpassenger area and used messaging that
OL,8,Fdid not reflect the customer
OL,9,Fexperience PoJ expects from all
OL,10,Foperators at the airport.
OL,12,F"The sign has been removed. To avoid
OL,13,Funexpected charges, passengers are
OL,14,Fencouraged to check their airline's
OL,15,Fbaggage policies in advance of travel."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
